      <title>英国水务主管称污水排放罚款将损害投资</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-21/uk-water-bosses-say-government-spill-plans-will-kill-investment</link>
      <description><![CDATA[行业老板警告说，政府提议阻止水务公司因污水泄漏支付股息，这将对修复英国日渐衰败的管道网络所需的投资产生灾难性影响。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-21/uk-water-bosses-say-government-spill-plans-will-kill-investment</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 21 Feb 2024 10:29:26 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国收紧对股票的管控，禁止开盘、收盘净售</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-21/china-tightens-grip-on-stocks-with-net-sale-ban-at-open-close</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国已禁止主要机构投资者在每个交易日开盘和收盘时减持股票，这是政府为支撑中国 8.6 万亿美元股市而采取的最有力举措的一部分。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-21/china-tightens-grip-on-stocks-with-net-sale-ban-at-open-close</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 21 Feb 2024 10:26:08 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
